snippet.title: Stuntfest - World Tour | Summer of Stunts Trailer
snippet.description:
Join the Summer of Stunts by taking part in our free playtest this weekend! 

Race, bounce and eject yourself through an elimination-based tournament and show that you really are the best of the fest. 

Keep in mind that the Summer of Stunts build is a very early version of Stuntfest, which likely won't reflect the final product

Stuntfest is coming to PC soon!
 
- Links & Info - 
Steam: https://thqn.net/stunt-steam 
Website: http://stuntfestgame.com 
Discord: http://discord.gg/stuntfest
